<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٦٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1547">حَفْصُ بْنُ عُمَرَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">الْأَسْوَدِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقْرَأُ: ﴿فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ﴾»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>